 207:../Middlewares/threadx/ports/cortex_m55/gnu/inc/tx_port.h **** /* Define the clock source for trace event entry time stamp. The following two item are port specif
 208:../Middlewares/threadx/ports/cortex_m55/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    For example, if the time source is at the address 0x0a800024 and is 16-bits in size, the clock
